Dialogue: 100,0:00:08.44,0:00:09.89,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,A venit momentul.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.75,0:00:18.85,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,Ce a fost asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:31.53,0:00:33.57,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,Au reușit să se trezească.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.50,0:00:41.59,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,De ce nu se aliniază?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:50.90,0:00:52.49,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,Pădurea este în pericol!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.71,0:01:11.30,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,O voi face eu, Argint.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.24,0:01:15.56,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Serios, mă descurc și singură.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:16.04,0:01:17.29,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Voi fi în regulă.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:22.97,0:01:24.18,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Ce tot faceți?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.80,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Oh, Elias.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.80,0:01:27.23,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Bună dimineața.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.58,0:01:30.89,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Mătase, stai, stai.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.58,0:01:34.93,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Voi merge la facultate curând, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.93,0:01:37.25,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Deci încerc să mă pregătesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.16,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Curând?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.44,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Adică în septembrie?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:40.78,0:01:42.82,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Mai sunt încă două luni până atunci.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.34,0:01:47.01,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Se pare că am nevoie de \No uniformă înainte de toate.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.01,0:01:48.60,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Măsurile mele...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.34,0:01:53.71,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Doar las-o pe Argint să se ocupe.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.54,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Știu, dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:57.33,0:01:59.15,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Vreau să mă obișnuiesc cu această mână.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.02,0:02:04.97,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,I was hoping to be more self-sufficient.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.47,0:02:08.99,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,Las-o în seama unui profesionist. E mai rapid așa.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:08.99,0:02:09.78,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:11.74,0:02:13.88,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Mersi, Mătase.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.88,0:02:15.26,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Ce vei face cu aia?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.72,0:02:19.40,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Trebuie doar să trimit această scrisoare facultății, iar ei îmi vor trimite uniforma.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.95,0:02:22.71,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,Are you upset that you don't get to make it?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:24.36,0:02:26.50,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, Silky.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.50,0:02:28.03,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Those are the rules, apparently.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.55,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Have you grown?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.78,0:02:37.95,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,You were about this tall \Nwhen you just got here.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.95,0:02:40.07,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Was I?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:40.07,0:02:42.34,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.46,0:02:46.81,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,I don't really feel taller.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:46.81,0:02:47.61,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.22,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,I've gotten just a little closer to you.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.28,0:02:55.43,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.34,0:03:01.43,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,It's a bit like a sailor uniform.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.91,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Sort of like the uniform \NI was wearing in Japan.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.64,0:03:08.48,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd be \Nwearing a uniform again.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.82,0:03:13.38,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I haven't \Nasked you about school.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.79,0:03:17.14,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,I don't have that many \Ngood memories to share.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.56,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,I'm still a little scared,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.01,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,but I'm excited to wear this uniform.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.26,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Just a second.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.33,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.83,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Chise, your body's cold.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.77,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,You don't feel well, do you?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.77,0:03:59.06,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,It seemed like you didn't get any sleep \Nbecause of that thunder last night.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.06,0:04:00.18,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.18,0:04:02.83,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,That was definitely \Na vicious storm last night.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.41,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Maybe I have a cold.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.22,0:04:07.25,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Get some rest.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.25,0:04:09.69,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,You won't get better staying awake.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.09,0:04:11.06,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.15,0:04:42.18,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Last night's severe storm has \Nstopped over central England.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.56,0:04:44.20,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,This, and this, and...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.18,0:04:44.67,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}The weather is predicted to \Nremain unstable for some time.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.94,0:04:45.86,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.35,0:04:49.55,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Everyone should check to see if anything in their house got covered in dust.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.39,0:04:47.27,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.02,0:04:54.29,Default,Radio,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Because we just had a storm...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:51.31,0:04:52.90,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Oh! That, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.76,0:05:02.58,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Okay,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.89,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,that's everything.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.28,0:05:12.51,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Are you telling me your\Njob is more important than mine?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.51,0:05:14.51,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Would you stop shouting?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.51,0:05:17.94,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted from going back and \Nforth to the hospital in London.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.94,0:05:19.99,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, so am I.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.99,0:05:23.36,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Damn it, this wouldn't be a problem \Nif we lived in London proper...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.36,0:05:26.97,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Gabriel would have gotten \Nworse if we'd stayed there.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.97,0:05:28.30,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.50,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I told you not to shout!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.50,0:05:32.22,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You're shouting louder!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.22,0:05:34.82,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Fantastic, so we're even, then!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.82,0:05:35.93,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.48,0:05:47.59,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Man, it's rough.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.94,0:05:50.98,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,It's way more rural here than I thought.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.74,0:05:53.32,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.36,0:05:56.26,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,It's really just the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.58,0:06:01.83,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I was hoping the scenery would at least \Nbe a bit more mystical, y'know?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.83,0:06:05.78,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Old forests, stone circles where giants \Nwould have shown up, stuff like that.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.23,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,There's none of it.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.23,0:06:09.27,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Seriously, nothing mystical at all.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.65,0:06:14.46,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I mean, I don't know this place, \Nso I guess I can explore a bit.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.46,0:06:15.47,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.93,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I'm hiding from Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.93,0:06:20.51,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,They're so annoying. I can't deal with them.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.47,0:06:26.38,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.38,0:06:30.21,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,The only thing that's better than London \Nis the treehouse in the backyard.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.35,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.92,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,There's a treehouse here.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.36,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Come check it out, Oscar.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.36,0:06:37.83,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,This weekend, maybe?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.12,0:06:41.24,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,There are some historic sites nearby, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.24,0:06:43.69,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,We might find something weird.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.69,0:06:46.59,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Like faeries, or haunted \Ncemeteries, or something.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.97,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.61,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Nah, that's fair.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.61,0:06:55.38,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Your mom and dad are busy.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.99,0:06:56.89,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.88,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,But you've gotta come\N over sometime, yeah?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.88,0:07:00.68,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,At least once during the summer break.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.11,0:07:01.89,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.89,0:07:03.02,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.68,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I'll call you.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.68,0:07:05.77,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.92,0:07:13.53,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Some journey this is...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.83,0:07:16.71,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You always do this when\Nyou don't get your way.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.71,0:07:20.20,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,That's because you never listen to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.20,0:07:23.34,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You're always just thinking about yourself.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.64,0:07:23.26,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,They're still at it.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.34,0:07:24.83,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'm thinking about this rationally!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.19,0:07:26.09,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Smoke?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.19,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.99,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Maybe I'm seeing things.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.64,0:07:40.77,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Wait, that's where lightning \Nstruck last night.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.29,0:08:03.61,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,No running!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.61,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.62,0:08:08.12,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,You were watching?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.62,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Are you going out?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.14,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Yeah, just going for a walk.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.46,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Where's your medication?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.32,0:08:14.43,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.18,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Keep it around your neck.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.59,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.59,0:08:19.02,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It's for your own good.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.35,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I'm not a kid anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.84,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,If you aren't a kid, you \Nought to understand.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.84,0:08:25.81,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I said, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.78,0:08:31.88,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,What's her problem?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.88,0:08:33.53,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,She drags me out to the countryside,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.70,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,gets into fights, and blames\N it all on my sickness.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.70,0:08:38.71,Default,A,0,0,0,,Oh man, that's a record!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.71,0:08:39.79,Default,B,0,0,0,,Focus! Focus!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.79,0:08:40.87,Default,C,0,0,0,,Seriously? Damn!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.28,0:08:42.45,Default,A,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.45,0:08:43.61,Default,C,0,0,0,,You've got this!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.61,0:08:45.38,Default,B,0,0,0,,Go for world record!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.68,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,It was around here, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.23,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,It's part of a stone circle!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.52,0:09:12.96,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,It's chipped.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.94,0:09:30.49,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,It'll be pretty with a little polish.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.91,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Crap, it's getting late.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.87,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,To think the Wild Hunt would \Nhave wandered so far...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.51,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.29,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,You've been separated from your master.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:24.27,0:10:26.28,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,Still cold, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.28,0:10:27.77,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Yeah, a little.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.28,0:10:30.97,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Maybe you should rest a little longer.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.97,0:10:33.36,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,I think I've slept too much.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.62,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Silver?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.62,0:10:37.16,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Stay put.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:37.16,0:10:38.50,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.80,0:10:45.34,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,How unusual.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.37,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,What's your business?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.61,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,I merely brought a stray.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.44,0:10:53.96,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:54.21,0:10:55.91,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,This is per its request.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:55.91,0:10:58.72,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,I need to get back to the forest.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.60,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with the forest?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:00.60,0:11:03.72,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,The Wild Hunt woke up and trampled it.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.34,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Wild Hunt?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.34,0:11:06.32,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.15,0:11:08.95,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:08.95,0:11:11.87,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,You don't have to come out, Chise.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:11.87,0:11:13.94,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,She isn't dressed appropriately \Nfor the mid-summer.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:14.18,0:11:16.52,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,I've had chills since this morning.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:16.52,0:11:19.81,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,That, too, is the influence of \Nthe wandering Wild Hunt.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:20.10,0:11:23.99,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,They've lost their way, and \Nare wandering this land.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.94,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,They're behaving differently than they should.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.04,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,Their steps are erratic.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.54,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,They wandered into the forest \Nwithout forming ranks,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:30.54,0:11:31.82,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,and trampled it.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:32.98,0:11:35.42,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,This one seems to have been \Nseparated from its master.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.72,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:38.35,0:11:39.09,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:42.92,0:11:45.83,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,The same thing is happening \Nall over the forest.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:46.42,0:11:50.03,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,If this returns, it may bring \Norder back to the Wild Hunt.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:50.85,0:11:52.22,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,I'll leave you to deal with it.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.62,0:11:55.10,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,I have my hands full taking \Ncare of the forest.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.52,Default,Spriggan,0,0,0,,Ask it to learn more.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.21,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:05.65,0:12:06.71,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:09.15,0:12:12.09,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Elias, what is the Wild Hunt?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.34,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,I'll explain inside.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.70,0:12:19.80,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Silky, tea and something \Nwith plenty of calories.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.73,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,There's a horse in the house.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:25.19,0:12:28.72,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,They are a band of knights \Nthat arrives with a storm
Dialogue: 100,0:12:29.52,0:12:34.31,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,near the summer solstice every twenty \Nor thirty seasons, to hunt horses.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:34.93,0:12:37.68,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,They leave death in their wake.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.12,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Death?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:39.47,0:12:42.11,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Old branches and weeds are culled,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:42.11,0:12:46.08,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,allowing for new branches \Nand buds to emerge.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:46.77,0:12:50.19,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Although it's not clear if that\Nis the Wild Hunt's original purpose.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:50.74,0:12:53.26,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,And this one was separated from that band?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.83,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,That seems to be the case.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:55.31,0:12:56.92,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Now, what should we do?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:56.92,0:12:59.09,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,How are we supposed to ask it anything?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.86,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Is there something you \Nwant to talk to us about?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:04.99,0:13:07.04,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Sorry, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:07.04,0:13:08.13,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,"I want to go home."
Dialogue: 100,0:13:09.35,0:13:11.97,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,He said he wants to go home.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.42,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,You can understand, Ruth?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:13.78,0:13:15.23,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,Kind of.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:15.23,0:13:18.30,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,Back when I was alive, I would talk \Nto the horses on the farm sometimes.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:18.67,0:13:20.34,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Ruth.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:20.62,0:13:23.23,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Were you a sheep dog or something?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:24.92,0:13:26.74,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Ruth, please.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:26.74,0:13:27.56,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.28,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,Talk.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.81,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,"We were in a slumber.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:35.67,0:13:40.09,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,We waited together with our \Nfriends inside a single boulder.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:40.78,0:13:44.56,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,When the time would come, we would \Nrun together to the promised land.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:45.61,0:13:47.67,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,Now was to be that time.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:49.51,0:13:54.15,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,Lightning split us apart, and I \Nwas separated from my friends.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:55.82,0:13:58.09,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,I am their leader.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:58.51,0:13:59.84,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,I must return.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:00.87,0:14:04.14,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,A knight and a horse \Ntogether make up a leader.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:05.35,0:14:09.19,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,That knight... {\i1}My{\i0} knight... \Nis nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:10.25,0:14:12.03,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,Help me find my knight.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:13.33,0:14:18.26,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,Or else my friends will become night \Nthieves, with no mind but to destroy the lands.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:19.51,0:14:24.28,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,Once I am reunited with my \Nknight, I will repay you."
Dialogue: 100,0:14:25.18,0:14:27.91,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,You've gotten lost all by yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.13,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Lightning, eh?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.89,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Now we also know why you've been ill.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:33.49,0:14:37.38,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,So we need to find his knight, first.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.98,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Chise, your body isn't stable yet.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.90,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Promise me you'll be careful.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:43.90,0:14:44.88,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:46.09,0:14:47.43,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:47.43,0:14:49.52,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,I'm already getting chills again.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:51.03,0:14:52.58,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,Let's start tomorrow.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:52.58,0:14:55.01,Default,Elias,0,0,0,,You ought to lie down immediately.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:55.01,0:14:56.00,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.66,Default,Ruth,0,0,0,,I don't think he can wait.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:59.93,0:15:03.23,Default,Chise,0,0,0,,Sorry, we'll leave in the morning.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.01,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:11.58,0:15:14.52,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,A well-polished stone bears power.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:14.52,0:15:16.64,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,That's what this book says, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:16.64,0:15:19.00,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I might even be able to summon some spirits.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:32.63,0:15:33.71,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.04,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.52,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Was that my imagination?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:47.13,0:15:48.54,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Wh-When did you get here?!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.90,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:52.90,0:15:55.20,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,What are you doing here so late at night?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.75,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,I'm lost.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.22,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,I have to go back.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:59.62,0:16:01.44,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Y-You're lost?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.31,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Should I call the police?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:03.68,0:16:04.22,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.41,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:06.41,0:16:07.84,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Is it busted?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:09.05,0:16:10.31,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Crap, it's Mom.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.62,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Gabriel!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:13.30,0:16:15.48,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Are you all right? I heard a loud noise.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:17.47,0:16:19.28,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:19.49,0:16:21.24,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:22.36,0:16:23.99,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.55,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:29.55,0:16:32.18,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What are you doing up so late, anyway?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:32.18,0:16:34.12,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You've been polishing \Nrocks again, haven't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:34.45,0:16:36.12,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.53,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It's late!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:37.53,0:16:40.69,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,We might not notice if \Nsomething happens to you.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.93,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doar eu îl pot vedea?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:44.93,0:16:45.93,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:46.58,0:16:47.72,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,D-Da!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:47.72,0:16:49.98,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,There's another storm coming, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:50.29,0:16:53.48,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You know you tend to have your attacks \Nwhen the weather's not good.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.56,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Am înțeles, mamă.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:55.56,0:16:56.93,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Asta e tot?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.07,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I'll go back as soon as \NI'm done cleaning up.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:59.07,0:17:00.94,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,You can go back inside.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:00.94,0:17:03.49,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I'll wait until you're back in your room.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:04.11,0:17:06.31,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I can't leave my equipment here.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:06.31,0:17:07.20,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I have to clean it up.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.74,0:17:10.57,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Five minutes.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:10.57,0:17:11.39,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.77,0:17:13.94,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Go wait at the door, Mom.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:13.94,0:17:16.20,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I have an early morning, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.24,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:17.24,0:17:18.60,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:24.95,0:17:25.72,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:27.05,0:17:27.98,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:31.82,0:17:34.03,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,You're a spirit, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.52,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.52,0:17:38.55,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Mom couldn't see you, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:38.55,0:17:39.45,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,What kind of spirit?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.22,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,The earth?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:40.22,0:17:41.11,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,The wind?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:41.11,0:17:43.00,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Or an ancient god?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.42,0:17:46.79,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Oh man, I can't believe I get\N to meet a real spirit.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.76,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's because \NI polished that rock.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.75,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:51.44,0:17:53.60,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,I don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:53.85,0:17:57.10,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Do you have amnesia?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.81,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,But I have to get back.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.48,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,I have to get back...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:06.24,0:18:08.85,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Hey, should I help you?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.44,0:18:12.04,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,But in exchange, can you be my friend?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:12.38,0:18:13.36,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,Friend?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.99,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,What, you don't wanna?!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:14.99,0:18:18.00,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,Uh, that's not it...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.33,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,It's settled, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:20.47,0:18:23.44,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I have to find out what kind \Nof spirit you are, first.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:23.77,0:18:26.45,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I think it's around here somewhere...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:26.45,0:18:27.49,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.58,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,What's that rock?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.58,0:18:30.78,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.07,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I picked it up today.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:32.07,0:18:33.83,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I'm still in the middle of polishing it.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.11,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Wanna try touching it?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:37.52,0:18:38.20,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:41.81,0:18:43.23,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Did you remember something?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:43.97,0:18:44.98,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:44.98,0:18:46.09,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.02,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Huh? Did something just...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.45,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:01.19,0:19:02.92,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:08.86,0:19:09.96,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:09.96,0:19:10.93,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.73,Default,Knight,0,0,0,,Are you really okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:13.73,0:19:14.43,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.80,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:16.12,0:19:19.53,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I cough when I exercise or get excited.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:21.55,0:19:23.78,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,It's always "don't do this, \Ndon't do that"...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:23.78,0:19:27.97,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Even when I'm hanging out with friends, \Nit's "don't run," "don't get dirty"...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:28.87,0:19:31.07,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,But I'm the only one who can see you.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:31.07,0:19:33.75,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Mom wouldn't get angry at \Nsomething she can't see.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:33.75,0:19:36.19,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Cred că vom fi buni prieteni.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:42.96,0:19:45.78,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Do you always have that on you?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:46.44,0:19:47.50,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Just like me.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:48.39,0:19:51.12,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,I keep this on my neck, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:56.20,0:19:57.43,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Gabriel!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:57.43,0:19:58.38,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Mai ai?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.92,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Fir-ar, trebuie să plec.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.88,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Poți dormi aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:03.45,0:20:06.19,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Haide să-ți căutăm casa mâine.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:06.19,0:20:08.37,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Îmi promit că ți-o voi găsi.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.21,Default,Gabriel,0,0,0,,Ne vedem mâine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:06.96,Magus-Ep_Title,,0,0,0,,Mireasa magicianului străvechi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:06.96,Magus-Ep_Title,,0,0,0,,Băiatul din Vest și cavalerul Furtunii Albastre
